Package: TweetLocViz
Type: Package
Title: Twitter Topic Modeling and Visualization for R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andreas Buchmueller
Maintainer: Andreas Buchmueller <a.buchmueller@stud.uni-goettingen.de>
Description: TLVIS is tailored for Twitter topic modeling tasks and visualization in R. 
    It can be used to collect, pre-process and analyze the contents of Tweets using 
    LDA and STM models. It also comes with visualizing capabilites like hashtag maps 
    and support for LDAvis.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/abuchmueller/TweetLocViz
